      <title>BC Partners 即将将 Synthon 出售给高盛资产管理公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bc-partners-is-said-to-near-sale-of-synthon-to-goldman-asset-arm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，BC Partners 即将达成协议，将荷兰仿制药制造商 Synthon International Holding BV 出售给高盛资产管理公司。]]></description>
