      <title>欧洲央行哈萨克斯坦官员警告不要过度降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/ecb-s-kazaks-warns-against-going-too-far-with-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行应该进一步降低利率，但可能不需要将利率降至刺激经济扩张的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/ecb-s-kazaks-warns-against-going-too-far-with-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿曼 OQ 甲醇部门首次公开募股 (IPO) 募资 4.89 亿美元后首日下跌 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/oman-oq-methanol-unit-falls-10-in-debut-after-489-million-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OQ Base Industries 在马斯喀特进行 4.89 亿美元的首次公开募股后，其股价在首日交易中下跌，这是中东地区一系列早盘交易不佳的上市公司中最新的一家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/oman-oq-methanol-unit-falls-10-in-debut-after-489-million-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 07:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据英国《金融时报》报道，蓝鲸因人工智能成本削减科技巨头股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/blue-whale-cuts-stakes-in-tech-giants-over-ai-costs-ft-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》报道，由于担心人工智能的成本，蓝鲸资本有限责任公司投资基金减持了美国主要科技公司的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/blue-whale-cuts-stakes-in-tech-giants-over-ai-costs-ft-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 06:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行誓言在政治动荡中稳定市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自韩国立法者投票弹劾总统尹锡烈以来，韩国央行首次发表声明，誓言要稳定金融市场，并强调“不间断实施”关键财政和经济措施的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国监管机构誓言稳定房地产和股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在高层领导人会议呼吁加大刺激措施之后，中国监管机构承诺加大力度稳定房地产和股市，并实施更有效的财政政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 04:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强、特朗普风险影响亚洲投资者 2025 年最佳投资方向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/strong-dollar-trump-risks-shape-asia-investors-top-2025-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球基金正在探索将新经济与旧经济相融合的方法，以保护其在2025年的亚洲投资免受美国贸易政策不确定性和美元走强的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/strong-dollar-trump-risks-shape-asia-investors-top-2025-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
